fy_scrapyard
*Info/Story* A small map, slightly S.T.A.L.K.E.R. inspirated map. "Story" is two factions that is fighting each other to control the scrapyard. The CT,s is holding the scrapyard and have a little camp there by the road. The T,s are coming from a sewer nearby and trying to attack the CT,s. May the best faction win!
*File info* Everything you need is packed in the bsp file. List: *Custom radar *A few custom textures *Color correction *Bot navigation file
*Install* Put the file "fy_scrapyard.bsp" in example: C:\Program\Steam\steamapps\"Your Account"\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps" and then just play!
